## Tips before your men's grooming visit in Srinagar

A little preparation helps your session go smoothly and comfortably:

- **Choose a well-lit room** with a chair, mirror access, and space for the stylist to work.
- **Have a towel and access to a wash basin** if hair wash is included in your booking.
- **Describe your preferred style** — or share a reference photo — when booking or at the start of the visit.
- **Book group grooming early** for weddings and Eid when demand is highest.
- **Be home or have the person receiving service available** at the confirmed time.

If anyone has skin sensitivity or allergies to hair products, mention this when you book so the stylist can plan accordingly. For event grooming, scheduling a day ahead of the function allows time for any adjustments.

